	<string name="about_text">
		<b>Pāli Platform Meditation Timer (S)</b> 1.0.1\n
		<small>(Simple Player version)</small>\n
		<small>Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0</small>\n
		\n
		<i>A minimalist but usable med-timer</i>\n
		<small>• Only core Android library is used, up to API level 19\n
		• Android 4.4 is the minimum requirement\n
		• The program should also work in modern Androids\n
		• If necessary, the app\'s restriction has to be disabled or running in background has to be allowed\n
		• If anything fails, please keep the screen on\n
		\n
		<b>Simple uses:</b>\n
		• Go to Settings\n
		• Select an interval between 5-20 minutes\n
		• Select a repeat up to 6 times\n
		• Select if tailing clicks are also added\n
		• Select if voice (TTS) markers are used\n
		• Select if the 20-sec preparation is used\n
		• Select if the device is kept awake\n
		• Go to Timer and press START\n
		• The session can be paused and resumed\n
		• Press the reset button to cancel the session\n
		• The settings are saved for the next use\n
		• Long press the reset button to restore the default settings\n
		• Use Live mode to arbitrarily ring bells\n
		</small>
